{"id":"cbd54315-aae8-43b7-b195-5b8ff201cf00","title":"1548/05/02: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"bcaab8eb-992d-46e6-a654-48df263e7856","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [May 2nd, 1548].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"cee634f5-dd2f-4aa4-8f9b-bf38659e8ee9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a0325baa-112a-420e-af7e-e56db2578f3a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8da15463-2a6a-45ce-8cc1-135a3c51c71a","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":24,"value":"45c2aace-5d11-4830-b500-9ef3084d06bf","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"061ec996-d2b6-43fe-b63b-61d170627df9","type":"style/superscript","start":17,"end":18,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"73336dad-d451-4fbb-ad79-3f991b1a8e1a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5a349da1-c373-47cf-b84e-0b6dad986b0d","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1149687b-0d83-4db7-9eb6-fb922f41dae5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2304e754-25d8-4c5a-a5af-26d2d1b75f01","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"7c724f98-abda-455f-81e1-b4e8678b62f3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"55dd6566-a260-4018-b8cc-a04f3111b06b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"cc199a27-0e06-4c45-a893-5f6b7301c98b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"3a6895bc-1852-40e0-a656-0d9f3388900b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo, \u2014 I have received the small barrel [caratello] of pears; there were 86 in all. I sent 33 of them to the Pope, who thought them very excellent and was greatly pleased with the present. But as to\u00A0the small barrel of cheese, the officer of the customs [dogana] tells me that the carrier is a rogue and that the cheese never got as far as his office. If I can find out whether he is in Rome I will see that he gets his\u00A0deserts; not on account of the cheese but so as to teach him not to value his fellow men so cheaply. I\u00A0have been very ill these last few days with dysuria, and for that reason I am still far from well: however, I am now better than I was. I tell thee this lest some gossipping person should write thee a whole tissue of\u00A0lies and give thee a fright. Tell the priest not to address me any more as Michelagnolo scultore, for I am not known here by any other name than that of Michelagniolo Buonarroti; tell him also that if there is a Florentine who wishes to have an altar-picture\u00A0painted he had better go and find a painter to do the work. I was never either a painter or a sculptor like\u00A0a shop-keeper. I have ever been careful for the honour of my father and of my brothers, although I\u00A0have served three Popes, having been obliged to do so. There is nothing more to add. Thou wilt have learnt what I think about the damsel from my letter written on the last day of last month. Do not tell the priest anything of what I have said about him in this\u00A0letter: I shall pretend not to have received his.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"dba3ffef-d96c-4f85-ac9e-15db0466cd21","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"aa1392dc-d2b2-44a6-8abb-7e59ab4e28fa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b